Genie: Generative Interactive Environments
Jake Bruce*,1, Michael Dennis*,1, Ashley Edwards*,1, Jack Parker-Holder*,1, Yuge (Jimmy) Shi*,1, Edward Hughes1, Matthew Lai1, Aditi Mavalankar1, Richie Steigerwald1, Chris Apps1, Yusuf Aytar1, Sarah Bechtle1, Feryal Behbahani1, Stephanie Chan1, Nicolas Heess1, Lucy Gonzalez1, Simon Osindero1, Sherjil Ozair1, Scott Reed1, Jingwei Zhang1, Konrad Zolna1, Jeff Clune1,2, Nando de Freitas1, Satinder Singh1 and Tim Rockt√§schel*,1
